Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.96,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.63,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A visitor from France!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.73,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Murderous intent harmonizes with the melody of the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.39,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.01,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.39,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{\fad(0,42)}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:29.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Created by\NGosho Aoyama\N"Detective Conan"\NSerialized in Shogakukan's\N'Weekly Shonen Sunday'
