Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana Azuki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Nakamura
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirohito Furui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:52.46,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Editor\NTeramitsu Okada\N \NStory Editor\NJun'ichi Iioka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:52.46,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Color Key\NReiko Hirayama\N \NExecutive Producer\NHiroaki Kobayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:03.39,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning Support\NToyohiko Okuyama\NMitome Asai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:07.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Director\NKenji Kodama\N \NDirector\NYasuichiro Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:21.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NMichihiko Suwa\N(Yomiuri TV)\NMasahito Yoshioka\N(Tokyo Movie)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kana Amusement Group\Nis a very big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshinori Kana (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would the chairman of such a company want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to be making a CD\Nfor Gerard Tenma at our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're going to be holding a private party upon the signing of the contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:27.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice! Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0} is finally going to make his debut in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:34.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a mysterious Japanese singer who is the talk of the French world of {\i1}chanson{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows anything about his personal history, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the day we decided on the date of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,eerie things have been happening around his wife Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eerie things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeated phone calls,\Nwith no one on the other end...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bouquet of roses from an unknown sender...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackmail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who do not realize my love will surely fall to the pits of hell..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We got the other one yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The curtains will be opened to commence the party of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy a party of terror to your heart's content..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The party will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't cancel it now,\Nbut I'm worried about my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who this may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carrying out the contract process in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the only ones who know that there is going to be a party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are my wife and I, and the other four who are scheduled to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:40.72,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:40.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"You left me behind all alone,\Nbut I still have not forgotten you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"My eyes are always on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I hear your voice and I am just so delighted."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:53.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Japanese lyrics to Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\N"The Red Nocturne of Love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:04:00.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hm... "I'll send you a flower a day..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:06.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"A red rose, a marigold, a lobelia,\Na bright red dahlia, and a love song..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"You are forever mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I wonder what she likes about a song like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that I'm going to get to see Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is work now, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be members of the Morita family, a friend of the chairman, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have them finding out that I'm a top-notch detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You two better behave yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} should be the one saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Going from the gate to the entrance of the house by car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is like what I've seen in foreign movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really some house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be millionaires!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:22.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't it look like a castle that you see in horror movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was such a fine day until just a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to see Gerard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being scared is another thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Morita-{\i1}sama{\i0}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:56.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:02.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-{\i1}san{\i0}! We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:09.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:23.59,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masayo Tokudaiji (24)\NSecretary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Masayo Tokudaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reception room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The artwork here is also fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my wife's taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:55.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, may I take a look around your residence before doing so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokudaiji-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:02.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my wife, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:14.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the president of the company group,\NKana Music Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.68,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki Kana (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prepare things in the kitchen, Masayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife doesn't like me, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the room right above the large reception hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond it is the piano room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You even have a spiral corridor in the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lay a finger on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all that fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's just a decoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's made of the same materials\Nand in the same way as the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In other words, it is the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The room next to the piano room is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:34.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This room also looks very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a picture of your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was taken ten years ago today, in Fiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:51.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We belonged to the same music club in our university days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We went steady for a year, and then got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this kind of thing happen often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a hoarse, male voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,things like "mon amie" and "je t'aime" are whispered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I answer, the phone is hung up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:38.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with a letter, I got this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this taken without you being aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I found together with the bunch of marigolds I found at the front door this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This seems to have been taken yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared because I feel like someone's always watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After the rose is the marigold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Always watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:11.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kogoro Mouri, will protect you,\NMisaki-{\i1}san{\i0}, with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, the guests have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, this is Gerard Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}'s manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Michel. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.59,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel Anglade (40)\NManager
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my older brother\NYoshinori Kana, and his wife Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. He had some other work to attend to,\Nso he'll be here about 30 minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:55.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an old friend of mine, Morita-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are his children, Ran-{\i1}san{\i0} and Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-{\i1}san{\i0}, this is my younger brother Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the vice-president of Kana Music Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.83,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Kana (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, may I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way and have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what delicious-looking dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't forget why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you invite outsiders here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important time when we have to sign a contract with Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave for France on your own and suddenly bring Gerard along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:38.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of the company, I don't see anything wrong in what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:43.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so, because if this doesn't work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't make yourself look good to Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been persistently hitting on Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you and Tokudaiji-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor's going around all over the company!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! There is nothing going on between her and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to make this contract go through, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for Gerard to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go wait for him by the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, I need to use the men's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get the next dish ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything to drink, Morita-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:39.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you excuse me while I go fix my make-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink too much, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to go guard Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Dad! You've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly go into a room where a lady is fixing her make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:11.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The power went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning hit somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody switched off the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Somebody suddenly attacked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lobelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as I thought, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}, flowers by that name come up in that song too, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That song?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "The Red Nocturne of Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose, marigold, lobelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that all the flowers that the person had sent up to now are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"My eyes are always on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear your voice and I am just so delighted."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that someone is threatening Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,according to the lyrics of Gerard Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that someone is stalking your beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:01.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know we are all in the midst of a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to question all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who turned off the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:11.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. On my way here, the breaker at the top of the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you at that time, Hideki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-{\i1}san{\i0}, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:22.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm not actually Morita, but Kogoro Mouri, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro... Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That famous...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0}, you locked the door, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I was about to fix my make-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:37.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the lights went out and I was attacked from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see the attacker's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see very clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was wearing a cape, and had a facial expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but where were you at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the front door to meet Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:06.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights went out and I came inside because it started to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Hideki-{\i1}san{\i0}, and heard a voice scream, "Help!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel-{\i1}san{\i0} is an important guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like the attacker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our main guest tonight, Gerard Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerard Tenma (34)\NChanson singer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There seemed to be no one downstairs, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a little incident here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I speak to you downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with me too, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The door of the room was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means the attacker was already in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Everyone who left the large reception hall beforehand had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:02.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So, who switched the breaker off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could there be more than one attacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is this a piece of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The crack is still new...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more small debris nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the size is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this a trace of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you all when the incident occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I panicked when the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:36.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the kitchen checking on the cake the mistress had baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}, you were drenched, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I got out of the taxi by the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we take a break then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:06.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:11.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, can you go get medicine from my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The picture that was taken last night was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They seem to have struggled pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0} and Gerard Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dated ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,two weeks before Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0} got married!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, Dad's going to scold you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, er, well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:52.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:06.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a relationship with Misaki in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, what a rude thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you knew about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why would I do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:18.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that before I married you, I was dating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His real name is Jun'ya Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}, and I used to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a nameless musician back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But on a certain day ten years ago, he suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw the papers for Gerard Tenma that we were going to sign a contract with,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to find that such a coincidence existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, I have a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hand-made wine, something that you cannot get in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to taste the wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be anything wrong with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's all have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She's still on her guard, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this sure is good wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! I was baking a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masayo-{\i1}san{\i0}, will you go to the basement in the yard and get me the silver tea set?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will serve you all a special hand-made cake I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As one of the conditions of having your company publish "The Red Nocturne of Love",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have slightly changed the lyrics and made a new arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A new arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerard insisted on doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this bunch of flowers at the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dahlias...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the language of flowers... Betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's secret, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}, won't you play your music for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're here in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You attacked Misaki, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not {\i1}that{\i0} again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could've done it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:54.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make preparations, so please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be having an argument...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tenma-{\i1}san{\i0}'s voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}T-This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:04.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"The Red Nocturne of Love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:09.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Mr. Tenma wrote this song for Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0} ten years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.24,0:24:13.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is this blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:15.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who attacked Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:30.58,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.58,0:24:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Wine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:40.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:36.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.79,0:24:37.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cha-ri-ra-ri-ra-rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:39.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's the sound of a case being solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.91,0:24:40.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I see.
